name: 8bit
description: 8bit offers a unique product in the form of an NFT collection of delightful cards with heroes of 8bit games. We are creating an ecosystem for connoisseurs of art by offering a purchase for an exclusive token - 8bit. Our mission is that our token is used as a universal reward for 8bit art, as well as become a part of the daily life of every fan of the 8bit era.
